\;\displaystyle{\frac{c^6 - 3}{c^2 + 2}}\;
(c^6 - 3)/(c^2 + 2)
c^2 + 2
11
c^2 = 9
c = \pm 3
\frac{c^6 - 3}{c^2 + 2} - (c^4 - 2c^2 + 4) = \frac{c^6 - 3}{c^2 + 2} - \frac{c^6 + 8}{c^2 + 2} = \frac{-11}{c^2 + 2},
\,c^2\!+2\mid \color{#0a0}{c^6\!-3}\,\Rightarrow\,
\,c^2\!+2\!:\,\ c^2\equiv \color{#c00}{ -2},\ \ \color{}0\equiv \color{#0a0}{(c^2)^3\!-3}\equiv (\color{#c00}{-2})^3\!-\!3 \equiv -11,\ 
\ c^2\!+2\mid 11.
